data.description: Completely renovated single family townhome.This two bedroom townhome has been completely renovated and is move-in ready! Upgrades include fresh paint and tile floors throughout, beautiful tray ceilings in the living room and main bedroom, granite counters in the kitchen and bath, and just wait until you see the walk-in shower!Both bedrooms share the newly updated main bathroom, which features an oversized single vanity granite countertop, and a modern brand new completely tiled shower with subway tiled walls and hexagon tiles on the floor for beautiful contrast. This home feels brand new when you walk inside! Located in the Green Acres area of Fort Walton Beach, convenient to the area's largest employers, including HCA Florida Fort Walton Destin Hospital, Eglin Air Force Base and Hurlburt Field. A quick trip to the grocery store or numerous big box retailers like Lowe's, Kohl's, or Target is incredibly easy and a short drive will take you to the area's sugar white sand beaches or the shopping, dining and nightlife of downtown Ft. Walton Beach in no time.
